_sText:
To install map, extract gg_high_low_2_Floor.vmt/bsp/etc into your /steamapps/<USERNAME>/counter-strike source/cstrike/maps/ folder. 



This map is more or less finished, but don't expect it to be the last! I will more than likely release a series of these; prettier and with more doo-dadds. please enjoy and comment! And please, I very much appreciate criticism as long as it's HELPFUL. Thanks for playing guys!
